   "author_association" : "MEMBER",
   "body" : "Global whitelist flags such as `-whitelistrelay` or `-whitelistforcerelay` should be removed in favour of per-peer flags `-whitelistrelay=$IP_ADDRESS` and `-whitelistforcerelay=$IP_ADDRESS`.\r\n\r\nOtherwise it is not possible to make fine-grained peer-specific settings about whitelisting and it is either \"all on\" or \"all off\" for all whitelisted peers.",
